OL,3,CUpper crust: Nottingham businesses
OL,4,Csweep British Pie Awards
OL,6,FTwo businesses in Nottingham have
OL,7,Ftaken top prizes at the British Pie
OL,8,FAwards this year.
OL,10,FThe best "pork pie of the year" was
OL,11,Fmade by Nottingham family butchers AE.
OL,12,FChamber Ltd, which beat 55 others
OL,13,Fhoping to receive the honour.
OL,15,FThe fourth-generation butchers also
OL,16,Ftook the prize in the same category
OL,17,Fjust two years ago, and is well-known
OL,18,Flocally for its handmade pastries -
OL,19,Fincluding its pork pies.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
