OL,3,CUpper crust: Nottingham businesses
OL,4,Csweep British Pie Awards
OL,6,FThe Cod's Scallops won top Fish & Chip
OL,7,FShop Pie with their Sunday Roast
OL,8,FChicken pie, beating 31 other entries.
OL,10,FThey're also no strangers to victory -
OL,11,Fhaving won best chip shop pie in 2019
OL,12,Ffor its Vegan Balti Pie.
OL,14,FThe annual event, which has been
OL,15,Frunning for 18 years, is hosted by the
OL,16,FMowbray Pork Pie Association, at St
OL,17,FMary's Church in Melton Mowbray in
OL,18,FLeicestershire.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
