OL,3,CUpper crust: Nottingham businesses
OL,4,Csweep British Pie Awards
OL,6,FThis year more than a thousand pies
OL,7,Fwere presented by 189 bakers from all
OL,8,Fover the UK with the aim of being
OL,9,Frecognised as the best.
OL,11,FThe top prize of Supreme Champion was
OL,12,Fawarded to Wigan pie maker Alexander
OL,13,FFlemming for his Chicken Kiev Pie.
OL,15,FA record 187 judges were recruited on
OL,16,Fthe panel, including pie buyers from
OL,17,FTesco and Sainsbury's, a selection of
OL,18,Festeemed food writers and journalists,
OL,19,Fand the 2015 Supreme Champion, Neil
OL,20,FBroomfield.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
