OL,3,CUpper crust: Nottingham businesses
OL,4,Csweep British Pie Awards
OL,6,FMatthew O'Callaghan, Chairman of the
OL,7,FMowbray Pork Pie Association and host
OL,8,Fof the British Pie Awards, said: "This
OL,9,Fyear's awards have been a stellar
OL,10,Ftribute to the nation's love of pies,
OL,11,Fwith a phenomenal atmosphere and, as
OL,12,Falways, oodles of creativity on
OL,13,Fdisplay.
OL,15,F"We had a wonderful day on Wednesday
OL,16,Fas we were given the important job of
OL,17,Fsampling some truly outstanding pies.
OL,26,@pD@bOUwD@AOU
